 XP System:
 - 10 XP per completion
 - 2x bonus at 7+ day streak
 - Levels: 1(0), 2(100), 3(250), 4(500), 5(850)... exponential curve
 - 8 badges: First Step, Week Warrior(7-streak), Month Master(30-streak), Centurion(100 tasks), Rising Star(lvl 5), Veteran(lvl 10), XP
 Hoarder(1000xp), Fortnight Focus(14-streak)

