 Verification Plan

 1. Smart Recurrence: Create tasks with Custom Weekly (Tue+Thu), Custom Monthly (1st+15th), Flexible (3/week). Verify monthly grid shows        
 correct applicable days. Verify stats calculation matches.
 2. Focus Mode: Click Focus on a task → timer starts → pause/resume → complete session → verify session saved.
 3. Gamification: Complete a task → verify XP increases. Build 7-day streak → verify 2x bonus. Check badges unlock correctly. Verify bestStreak 
  updates.
 4. Smart Reminders: Set morning reminder to current time → wait → verify notification fires. Set evening reminder → verify it shows remaining  
 tasks count.
 5. Reflections: Write today's reflection with mood → save → verify in calendar view. Navigate to past dates → verify read-only display. Check  
 dashboard prompt card.
 6. Build: Run npm run build to verify no build errors.
